ore":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:07:35.000Z","msg":"個集會係比西人睇，西人WFC義士咩情況"},{"pid":"24ab60b70ac9a6ba2117b2c426c7f89a9750bc39","tid":1259253,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"240846a57d29de143645fecc499d8e89ac22fda2","tid":1259253,"uid":148744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:07:35.000Z","msg":"個集會係比西人睇，西人WFC義士咩情況"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:20:58.000Z","msg":"即係依家加入第五大訴求啦係嗎？<br />\n<br />\n佢騎劫呢個集會若果去到最後係做出嚟嘅嘢令香港好嘅 我冇咩問題。 但事實上泛民又好，民陣都好所有爭取嘅嘢爭取到一半就停手。 有香港電視，真普選，高鐵等等每一次都係爭取到一半就停手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家四大訴求一樣都爭取唔到， 突然間變咗焦點， 咁同以前有乜嘢分別？<br />\n<br />\n如果佢哋學陳雲講自治，我冇問題。<br />\n但係佢哋呢一班人唔敢做到陳雲咁盡。<br />\n甚至乎會同提倡自治嗰班兄弟割席。 <br />\n再落去會同四大訴求嘅兄弟割席。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次一諗起呢度我就好心痛"},{"pid":"33385008c05873977536f6699620896897bcf44f","tid":1259253,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497e3c914fc2442b0abf56c4253681d6e8ca1a98","tid":1259253,"uid":128522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T14:27:07.000Z","msg":"頭先車場係咁叫釋放被捕人士<br />\n大台特登開大聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\